data.description: It's time to see 6348 Topeka Terrace. Nestled within the inviting gated community of Liberty Square. Offering privacy and a sense of security. This  GORGEOUS OPEN FLOOR PLAN is a 2 story home, has 3 Bedrooms and 2 1/2 Bathrooms. As you enter the home, you'll observe the high ceilings that create an open and spacious ambience. All bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs, providing a peaceful retreat away from the main living areas. The master bedroom is particularly impressive, boasting a generous size and featuring upgraded sink vanity, a luxurious soak bathtub, standalone walk-in shower and walk-in-closet.  In addition to the well-appointed master bedroom, there are two nicely sized bedrooms, perfectly for accommodating children, family and friends. Adjoining to the bedrooms, you'll find a conveniently placed laundry room, simplifying daily routines.  The newly remodeled Kitchen comes with a water-softener, breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. Additional features include a cozy fireplace, oversized baseboards, upgraded flooring, shutters throughout and tranquil porch setting. The gated community itself offers a range of amenities, including a BBQ grill area where you can gather with family and friends for outdoor cooking and dining. Additionally, there is a community park where you can enjoy leisure strolls, picnics, or simply relax in the serene environment. Located within a Distinguished School District. This BEAUTIFUL NEWLY REMODELED Home Checks all the Boxes, Your Home Search Is COMPLETE!
